roughcut.media.videoeditor

Class Effect

  • java.lang.Object
    • roughcut.media.videoeditor.Effect
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EffectColor, EffectKenBurns

    public abstract class Effect
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the super class for all effects. An effect can only be applied to a single media item.
